  "slug": "pungent-indian-kale-hyderabadi-pakora",
  "title": "Hyderabadi Kale Pakora",
  "description": "Crispy fritters made with kale and a blend of Indian spices. A classic Hyderabadi street food.",
  "cuisine": "Indian",
